  "name": "Morphic Mask",
  "type": "feat",
  "img": "systems/pf1/icons/skills/light_07.jpg",
  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>The vigilante’s physical form in his vigilante identity can differ significantly from that of his social identity, within the norms for his race—this can include changes to the vigilante’s proportions, coloration, gender characteristics, and other physical characteristics. This increases the vigilante’s bonus from seamless guise by 2 for every significant change, as per the Disguise skill. The vigilante always assumes the same form when using this ability.</p>\n<p>A vigilante with multiple natural forms, such as a&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.aonprd.com/RacesDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Kitsune\">kitsune</a>, can alter each of his forms using this talent.</p>",
